OL,3,CSon kept mum's body in freezer after
OL,4,Cher death three years ago
OL,6,FA son has admitted preventing the
OL,7,F"lawful and decent" burial of his
OL,8,Fmother after her body was found in a
OL,9,Ffreezer. He also admitted to
OL,10,Fwithdrawing money from her account.
OL,12,FChristopher Phillips, 60, was arrested
OL,13,Fafter the body of 89-year-old Sylvia
OL,14,FPhillips was discovered in a property
OL,15,Fin Porthcawl on 17 February.
OL,17,FA post mortem was carried out but a
OL,18,Fprovisional cause of death was not
OL,19,Fprovided yet, with further
OL,20,Finvestigation needed.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/3
