OL,3,CSon kept mum's body in freezer after
OL,4,Cher death three years ago
OL,6,FAppearing at Cardiff Crown Court on
OL,7,FThursday, 16 April, Mr Phillips
OL,8,Fadmitted preventing a lawful and
OL,9,Fdecent burial between 2 October 2022
OL,10,Fand 17 February this year.
OL,12,FThe court was told it is believed Mrs
OL,13,FPhillips died in 2023.
OL,15,FThe defendant also admitted to two
OL,16,Fcounts of fraud, after failing to
OL,17,Fdisclose to the Department for Work
OL,18,Fand Pensions and Bridgend Council that
OL,19,Fhis mother had died.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/3
