OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1776345056
OL,3,CSon kept mum's body in freezer after
OL,4,Cher death three years ago
OL,6,FMrs Phillips' body was found at an
OL,7,Faddress in Poplar Crescent after a
OL,8,Fcall was made to police about the
OL,9,Fwelfare of a woman.
OL,11,FDefence barrister Ruth Smith said her
OL,12,Fclient had entered a basis of plea and
OL,13,Fasked for sentencing to be adjourned
OL,14,Ffor a psychiatric report to be carried
OL,15,Fout.
OL,17,FThe Recorder of Cardiff, Judge Tracey
OL,18,FLloyd-Clarke adjourned Phillips'
OL,19,Fsentencing until 2 June.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/3
